实是霙完全不懂希美在想什么，那些心思都是霙没有过的，所以也不会想到，我觉得霙当时还是困惑的，为啥希美冒出这一句<br />\r\n于是，希美在霙的无意间又心碎了一次，不过失落和不甘都在后来的大笑中一定程度的释然，“既然明知道自己天分不够，还纠结这个做什么呢？”","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"917","username":"adonai","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"916","dbdateline":"1544115260","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41856783","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"astrayveller","authorid":"505868","dateline":"2018-12-7 00:57","message":"最后那个告白场景霙还有一个特别可爱的地方<br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201812/07/005715xpzjgj4ac2cpzre4.png\" attach=\"41856783\" /></div><br />\r\n这种“虽然不知道希美为什么笑但是她开心我就开心”的表情实在是太棒了好吗<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"918","username":"astrayveller","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"917","dbdateline":"1544115459","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41856807","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"astrayveller","authorid":"505868","dateline":"2018-12-7 01:00","message":"告白完之后还有两只鸟平行飞行 时而远离时而靠近的镜头 能说的东西真的不要太多 只能说山田尚子太会拍片了吧（","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"919","username":"astrayveller","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"918","dbdateline":"1544115629","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41856828","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"未来起航","authorid":"467117","dateline":"2018-12-7 01:05","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41856762&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">adonai 发表于 2018-12-7 00:54</font></a><br />\r\n霙说喜欢希美的一切，希美赶紧说喜欢霙的双簧管是希望得到霙的回应，也能说喜欢她的长笛，如果自己的长笛 ...</div><br />\n一个单纯阿宅，喜欢上一个扭曲现充。倒也般配<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"920","username":"未来起航","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"919","d